title: Elvis Presley’s grandkids in foster care
itunes:title: Elvis Presley’s grandkids in foster care
description:
Elvis Presley’s twin granddaughters are in foster care until a judge consider their safety in light of a shocking discovery inside their home, according to court documents. Lisa Marie Presley said in a sworn court filing she found “hundreds of inappropriate photos” and “disturbing video” on her estranged husband’s computers. Nancy Grace and Alan Duke discuss the revelations in this explode.
